:

1. *El* se smeškao i stavio ruku na rame. (He smiled and put his hand on his shoulder.)
2. Ona mu je poklonila *el*. (She gave him a scarf.)
3. On je uzeo *el* i malo počeo da pleše. (He took the scarf and started to dance a little.)
4. *El* je bio veoma lep i dugačak. (The scarf was very beautiful and long.)
5. *El* je bio u boji crvene boje. (The scarf was red in colour.)